query:
SELECT name, address, checkInDate, checkOutDate, FROM_UNIXTIME(checkInDate/1000) as checkIn, FROM_UNIXTIME(checkOutDate/1000) as checkOut 
FROM hotels 
WHERE tripId = 30001 
ORDER BY checkInDate ASC;
